Question: In LaTeX, you want to use the expected value symbol that appears as a double-lined E, commonly seen in statistical literature. Which of the following code snippets would correctly produce this symbol in your document?

A) \usepackage{amsmath}
   \newcommand{\E}{\mathbb{E}}

B) \usepackage{bbold}
